Radium Constrained Execution (RCE)

This directory contains the reference preprint describing the
Radium Constrained Execution runtime model.

Title:
Radium Constrained Execution (RCE): A Runtime Model for Governing Machine Actions

Author:
Majd Radium

DOI:
https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18906306

Canonical publication:
https://radiumdefense.org

This document introduces the RCE primitive for execution governance
in automated and distributed infrastructures.
